{"type": "article", "id": 27484, "title": "一不小心，你的人生是否又陷入了无限循环？", "description": "这就是生活啊！", "date": "2016-05-30T07:15:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 11405, "name": "好奇心研究所"}], "category": 3, "column": 33, "author": 130547, "comment_count": 22, "praise_count": 226, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703123925S96hPNxHguartenY.gif", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">好奇心研究所的微博（@好奇心研究所）和微信公众号（ID：QLab42）全面上线啦，关注就可以与所长亲密接触。  <br></p>\n<p class=\"\">我们发现，人生经常陷入一种很无奈的状况：先做错一件事－跳出来要求做另一件事－但所处的状况却不具备这种条件，结果就一错再错，陷入某个恶性循环。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>1. 丢了眼镜\r\n\r\n－\r\n\r\n找眼镜\r\n\r\n－\r\n\r\n然而看不清。<br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123915gJ4YaZzUHTyEMdso.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.558\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>2. 困\r\n\r\n－\r\n\r\n没效率\r\n\r\n－\r\n\r\n活没做完\r\n\r\n－\r\n\r\n熬夜\r\n\r\n－\r\n\r\n困\r\n\r\n－\r\n\r\n没效率\r\n\r\n－\r\n\r\n活没做完\r\n\r\n－\r\n\r\n熬夜\r\n\r\n－\r\n\r\n困……</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123916v6CmyUQA1buNjPto.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>3. 进屋只想一头倒在床上 －床很乱。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031239176io5pq2j0BryebC9.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.538\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>4. 选错专业\r\n\r\n－\r\n\r\n入错行。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031239178thaVG5qv0krTXn6.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.554\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p><b>5. 出门在外\r\n\r\n－\r\n\r\n手机欠费\r\n\r\n－\r\n\r\n断网\r\n\r\n－\r\n\r\n但没网就不能充话费。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123918JeiqVWrKaj1wLThn.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>6. 手残的人，想训练动手技能。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123918e53qM7Hs1NPECtaz.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>7. 想翻墙\r\n\r\n－\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n找翻墙教程\r\n\r\n－\r\n\r\n需要翻墙才能看。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123920lkxObFm08JGYzWr2.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56069364\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>8. 想解压\r\n\r\n－ 下载解压软件\r\n\r\n－需要解压。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123920932h1QSfrIXNP4BU.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>9. 老版 lumia 充电\r\n\r\n－\r\n\r\n开机\r\n\r\n－\r\n\r\n耗电\r\n\r\n－\r\n\r\n关机……<br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123921C6OWot9XTapGqr4M.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>10. 睡上铺\r\n\r\n－\r\n\r\n铺床单必须踩着床\r\n\r\n－\r\n\r\n但踩着就不好铺。<br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123922jzcnySUvYs8NXTb4.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8375\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p><b>11. 换新号码后\r\n\r\n －\r\n\r\n重新绑定应用\r\n\r\n －\r\n\r\n验证码发到旧号码。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123923goR1Td8mrlDPB3JM.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>12. 胖\r\n\r\n －\r\n\r\n不吃饭\r\n\r\n －\r\n\r\n坚持两天\r\n\r\n －\r\n\r\n太饿\r\n\r\n －没忍住大吃 －\r\n\r\n反弹。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123923dqetvjfnmzFGrY72.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>13. 爸妈打我\r\n\r\n－ \r\n\r\n不服气\r\n\r\n－ \r\n\r\n爸妈看我不服气\r\n\r\n－ \r\n\r\n又打我。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123924aXZduSK5On6PGHQR.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>14. 做错了一件事 －又做错一件事\r\n\r\n－再做错一件事……</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123925ig52oUe6tySVLKax.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure>\n</div>\n<p>动图来自：<a href=\"http://giphy.com/\">giphy</a></p>\n<p><i><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/labs.html\">好奇心研究所</a></i><em>是好奇心日报的一个调查栏目，这是一个探讨各种生活方式问题的互动平台，它针对的可能是生活方式的变化和潮流，也可能是某个品牌的服务。你可以在这里投票、吐槽、表明态度。</em></p>\n\n\n"}